{"word":"ἐπιπέτομαι","slug":"ἐπιπέτομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιπέτομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-πτήσομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>ἐπεπτάμην</el>) (or <el>-όμην</el>) (also in <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> form <el>ἐπέπτην</el>) (<a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>ἐπιπτάς</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to fly to</i> or <i>towards</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to fly over</i>, <el>πεδία</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li250'><b>B. </b><el>ἐφίπταμαι</el>, late <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> of <el>ἐπιπέτομαι</el>, <b><a href='S:Moschus'>Mosch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}